org.cougaar.core.qos.frame.aggregator
Interface SlotAggregator

All Known Implementing Classes:
Average
public interface SlotAggregator

Part of an experiment in generalizing slot dependencies. Implementations of this interface compute and set a slot value on some frame, given a collection of related frames, at least one of which has presumably changed in some way.
